Package: MBTAr
Type: Package
Title: Access Data from the Massachusetts Bay Transit Authority (MBTA) Web API
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: person("Justin", "de Benedictis-Kessner", email = "justindbk@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Depends:
  R (>= 3.1.2)
LazyData: true
Description: Access to the MBTA's GTFS-compatible API for R. Creates an easy-to-use
  bundle of functions to work with all the built-in calls to the MBTA API.
  Allows users to download realtime tracking data in dataframe format that is
  manipulable in standard R analytics functions. Pulls performance statistics
  in both realtime and for historical dates and trips (after July 2015).
License: GPL-3
Imports:
  jsonlite
